The data comes from `api.featureRegistry.Get()`, which returns `map[string]map[string]bool` — **outer key = category, inner key = feature name → enabled bool**. So the JSON is nested by category, e.g. `{"api": {"lifecycle": true, ...}, "otlp_receiver": {"delta_conversion": false}}`, not flat dotted names.

